{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/modify-koko-id/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b2edf43c-f822-5e8e-a1e8-02e2eb268e5b","excerpt":"去 MOPCON 不小心在國泰攤位辦了 KOKO 帳戶，都是為了現場拿電腦包 辦 KOKO 送的當肯電腦包  KOKO 帳戶兩天就通過了  可是我在使用 KOKO App 設定 KOKO ID 的時候手殘+眼殘不小心打錯字還設定了… 打過客服、網路上查、寫信去問都說不能改… 真的是 QQ 原本還以為 LINE ID…","html":"<p>去 MOPCON 不小心在國泰攤位辦了 KOKO 帳戶，都是為了現場拿電腦包</p>\n<h3>辦 KOKO 送的當肯電腦包</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"koko id 0\"\n        title=\"koko id 0\"\n        src=\"/static/5265a5cafaa9642c59750a6779c72c84/80e3c/koko-id-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5265a5cafaa9642c59750a6779c72c84/4ec73/koko-id-0.jpg 180w,\n/static/5265a5cafaa9642c59750a6779c72c84/158ba/koko-id-0.jpg 360w,\n/static/5265a5cafaa9642c59750a6779c72c84/80e3c/koko-id-0.jpg 720w,\n/static/5265a5cafaa9642c59750a6779c72c84/47311/koko-id-0.jpg 1080w,\n/static/5265a5cafaa9642c59750a6779c72c84/eea4a/koko-id-0.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>KOKO 帳戶兩天就通過了</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 591px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"koko id 1\"\n        title=\"koko id 1\"\n        src=\"/static/73bff6a33d358eec0459a82e46244693/5608a/koko-id-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/73bff6a33d358eec0459a82e46244693/4ec73/koko-id-1.jpg 180w,\n/static/73bff6a33d358eec0459a82e46244693/158ba/koko-id-1.jpg 360w,\n/static/73bff6a33d358eec0459a82e46244693/5608a/koko-id-1.jpg 591w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>可是我在使用 KOKO App 設定 KOKO ID 的時候手殘+眼殘不小心<strong>打錯字</strong>還設定了… 打過客服、網路上查、寫信去問都說不能改… 真的是 QQ 原本還以為 LINE ID 可以改，還嘴了一番，沒想到上網查也是不能改。</p>\n<p>都什麼年代了數位銀行的 ID 居然不能改？！上網想要銷戶還不能銷，問客服說要臨櫃才可以銷。OK, fine.</p>\n<p>昨天早上我就到國泰世華去辦理銷戶，行員看起來是第一次辦 KOKO 銷戶，還要查法規等等的，不過也沒花太久的時間就辦好了，現場有問行員是不是能重新申請，她說條文沒寫不行就是可以。過了半天昨天下午我的 KOKO App 就登不進去了，應該是銷戶成功了！</p>\n<p>晚上跟同事吃飯的閒聊時間順便重新申請一下 KOKO，今天早上就過了，而且這次 ID 設定對了 XD</p>\n<h3>新的 KOKO 帳戶</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 591px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 103.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"koko id 2\"\n        title=\"koko id 2\"\n        src=\"/static/e6baee90cde8609addb009b1a047c132/5608a/koko-id-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e6baee90cde8609addb009b1a047c132/4ec73/koko-id-2.jpg 180w,\n/static/e6baee90cde8609addb009b1a047c132/158ba/koko-id-2.jpg 360w,\n/static/e6baee90cde8609addb009b1a047c132/5608a/koko-id-2.jpg 591w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"國泰世華 KOKO ID 變更方法","date":"October 24, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/modify-koko-id/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/mopcon-2019/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"MOPCON 2019"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/github-slang/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TL;DR? LGTM? 什麼意思？"}}}}}